These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, fanta, juice
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, ferret, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea | juice | fanta |
| Pet        | bird | hedgehog   | frog | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, zombie, mystery, action
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, canadian, british, pakistani
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the british##1
3. the british is in an odd position##4
4. the malaysian is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the canadian is on the right of the british##1
6. the malaysian is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | adventure  | zombie  | action |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | malaysian | british | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, broccoli, nectarine, papaya
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, adventure, drama, thriller
1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
2. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | papaya | nectarine | broccoli    | pear      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama        | thriller     | time-travel | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, board-games, singing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, salsa, ambient, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the fan of soul and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the fan of ambient is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | card-games | board-games | singing |
| Music-Genre   | ambient       | soul   | salsa    | jazz  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, rock, soul, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian, mexican, chinese
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the chinese##1
2. the egyptian is the fan of ambient##1
3. the mexican is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
6. the japanese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | d&b    | soul   | ambient       |
| Nationality   | japanese | chinese | mexican | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, satire, horror, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, american, chinese
