2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the mexican##1
3. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
4. the dutch is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the american is on the left or right of the dutch##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror      | satire | sports | zombie |
| Nationality   | chinese | mexican     | dutch  | american  |

