.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, satire, thriller, fantasy
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, bike, van
1. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person driving the van is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | fantasy | thriller | satire    |
| Transport     | van | bike  | helicopter     | snowmobile |

