.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, analyst, dressmaker, chef
4 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, mouse, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the chef is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the chef##3
4. the chef is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the police-officer is between the chef and the analyst##2
6. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the chinchilla is between the police-officer and the owner of the mouse##2
8. the police-officer is on the left or right of the analyst##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | analyst | police-officer      | chef | dressmaker |
| Pet   | turtle  | lizard | chinchilla    | mouse            |

