.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lemon, onion, raspberry
4 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, bird, rabbit
1. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
2. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the person eating onion##2
4. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating onion is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | raspberry | lemon   | eggplant | onion |
| Pet    | rabbit     | goldfish | dog     | bird  |

