.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, gospel, classical, d&b
1. the person drinking water is the fan of d&b##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the fan of d&b is between the fan of indie and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea       | hot-chocolate   | water | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | classical | gospel | d&b        | indie    |

