.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, 7up, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk   | sprite   | cola      | 7up      |
| Sport      | lacrosse | snowboarding | weightlifting | basketball |

