.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, avocado, grapefruit, nectarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, r&b, electronic
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
3. the person eating avocado is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is between the fan of indie and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | nectarine | avocado  | grapefruit  | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b | dubstep | indie   |

