.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, camping, gardening, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, skiing, cricket
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's hobby is camping##2
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | reading | camping         | fishing   | gardening |
| Sport   | skiing    | handball | cricket | lacrosse   |

