.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, chess, cooking, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, badminton, parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
5. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | chess | photography | cooking    | puzzles |
| Sport   | rowing   | parkour  | sailing | badminton     |

