.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, dancing, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, australian, pakistani, russian
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
3. the australian is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the australian##3
5. the australian is between the russian and the pakistani##2
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games   | dancing | rock-climbing | magic-tricks    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | australian  | russian     | polish |

