.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, iced-tea, coffee
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, pomegranate, peach, apple
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating apple##1
5. the person eating apple is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
7. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | coffee | almond-milk    | iced-tea       | mirinda |
| Food       | pomegranate  | peach | apple | artichoke  |

