.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, mexican, brazilian, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, skateboard, bike
1. the argentine is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | argentine  | dutch |
| Transport     | taxi      | skateboard       | subway | bike     |

