.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, coach, police-officer
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, trike, scooter, car
1. the engineer is in an even position##4
2. the engineer is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the person driving the trike is between the accountant and the person driving the airplane##2
4. the engineer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the police-officer##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | accountant | coach   | police-officer | engineer |
| Transport   | car          | trike | airplane         | scooter  |

 